WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.640
Previously on Incorporated...

00:01.641 --> 00:05.107
- Take this. Bye, Aaron.
- I'll find you.

00:05.108 --> 00:07.287
- Aaron!
- Told you I'd find you.

00:07.288 --> 00:09.321
I just have so much
riding on this scholarship.

00:09.356 --> 00:11.257
But what about you?

00:11.258 --> 00:13.926
You may not realize your
dream of attending college.

00:13.962 --> 00:16.829
There could be a place for
you in the Spiga family.

00:16.864 --> 00:19.364
- Get away from my daughter.
- Okay.

00:19.400 --> 00:21.200
The guy who runs things
around here is named Tino,

00:21.235 --> 00:22.802
and I work for him. Your guy shoots,

00:22.837 --> 00:24.470
you don't make it to the wall alive.

00:24.505 --> 00:25.972
- What is this?
- $20,000.

00:26.007 --> 00:27.406
Where did you get this?

00:28.943 --> 00:31.276
My sister, she's a sex slave.
Where is she?

00:31.312 --> 00:32.645
- Arcadia.
- Can you get in here?

00:32.680 --> 00:34.379
Access is restricted to senior execs.

00:34.415 --> 00:35.194
I need a personnel file.

00:35.195 --> 00:37.850
This feels a little out of your
purview, doesn't it? Hendrick, right?

00:37.885 --> 00:39.518
Roger Caplan came to my office.

00:39.553 --> 00:40.786
I just need a little more time.

00:40.822 --> 00:42.421
This guy is onto you.

00:42.456 --> 00:44.023
I need you to get me into Arcadia.

00:44.058 --> 00:45.491
Who is it you're gunning for?

00:45.526 --> 00:47.893
There's someone standing in my way.

00:47.929 --> 00:49.328
- I have to go.
- Go? Wait...

00:49.363 --> 00:51.263
Presentation's at 1:00.

00:51.298 --> 00:55.101
I think he's connected
to one of the companions.

01:00.102 --> 01:03.854
12 YEARS AGO

01:05.841 --> 01:09.081
Hey, buck up, kid.

01:09.117 --> 01:11.416
I'm leaving you the shadow.

01:13.621 --> 01:15.721
There's a contact on the ghost drive...

01:15.757 --> 01:18.977
A guy named Tino, who will set you
up for work when you get out.

01:20.895 --> 01:22.628
I got you something too.

01:24.431 --> 01:26.699
It's a water key.

01:26.734 --> 01:29.748
Took me three days to get
through the metal yard for parts.

01:30.271 --> 01:34.740
It'll get you into any FEMA water truck.

01:34.776 --> 01:37.743
Well, if things don't
work out, I might need it.

01:37.779 --> 01:39.779
There won't be any water
trucks where I'm going...

01:39.814 --> 01:43.649
no rationing either, but this is good.

01:43.685 --> 01:46.886
This is really good.

01:46.921 --> 01:49.655
Thank you.

01:49.691 --> 01:51.924
Must be some back door you found.

01:51.959 --> 01:56.162
Yeah. Unfortunately, it's
about to close, so...

01:56.197 --> 01:58.097
I gotta go now.

02:00.702 --> 02:03.903
Hey...

02:05.472 --> 02:08.741
you're already better at
this than I ever was.

02:08.776 --> 02:12.344
Keep your head in the game.
You'll be fine. 'Kay?

02:12.379 --> 02:15.547
All visible religious
iconography, clothing,

02:15.583 --> 02:19.518
or headgear is strictly
prohibited in public spaces.

02:19.553 --> 02:20.786
Do me a favor?

02:23.157 --> 02:24.724
Check on Elena for me.

02:26.393 --> 02:28.327
Do yourself a favor.

02:28.362 --> 02:30.830
When you get out of
here, don't look back.

02:34.476 --> 02:38.121
6 YEARS AGO

02:39.841 --> 02:41.373
Hurry, please!

02:45.012 --> 02:47.312
What the hell are you waiting for?

02:47.348 --> 02:49.314
Restaurant didn't pay their bills.

02:49.350 --> 02:50.916
We're here to make sure that
the fire doesn't spread

02:50.952 --> 02:52.752
to the places that did.

02:52.787 --> 02:55.454
Are you fucking kidding me?

02:55.489 --> 02:57.823
Hey!

02:59.827 --> 03:02.494
Try that again, you get
the other side of the axe.

03:02.529 --> 03:05.965
No, no...

03:06.000 --> 03:07.466
No!

03:10.805 --> 03:13.939
You son of a bitch. You did this.

03:14.570 --> 03:15.307
No-no-no-no-no!

03:15.342 --> 03:16.809
Aaron didn't do anything.

03:16.844 --> 03:19.344
He scammed the money
exchange in broad daylight.

03:19.380 --> 03:20.946
You think I didn't hear about that?

03:20.982 --> 03:22.547
The whole neighborhood knows.

03:22.583 --> 03:24.549
We got caught in the crossfire,
because you shorted Tino

03:24.585 --> 03:27.186
and his cut, didn't you?

03:27.221 --> 03:30.322
Didn't you?

03:30.357 --> 03:32.557
You think Tino did this?

03:32.593 --> 03:35.627
Everything we built... it's gone.

03:35.663 --> 03:37.029
It's all gone.

